2006-10-01  Alexis Saettler  <asbin@asbin.org>

	* add configure script and update Makefiles

2006-01-22  Benjamin Zores  <ben@geexbox.org>

	* first inclusion of Open Media Center to GeeXboX Arch tree.
	* support for some generic widgets : image, text, menu, border,
	  clipper, cover, browser (files or MRLs/playlist),
	  Playing MRL notifier.
	* support for some screens : main screen, audio files selection screen,
	  video files selection screen, audio player screen.
	* audio player support with Xine
	* basic audio player controls.
	* cover and metadata support.
	* amazon.com search for CD/DVD covers.
	* support for playlists.
